Package: android-globalconfig-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Global config headers for all Android programs and libraries
 This package contains headers of various architectures that must be included
 by all Android C/C++ codes.

Package: zipalign
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Depends: android-libandroidfw,
         android-libcutils,
         android-liblog,
         android-libutils,
         libzopfli1,
         zlib1g,
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Zip archive alignment tool
 zipalign is an archive alignment tool that provides important optimization to
 Android application (.apk) files. The purpose is to ensure that all
 uncompressed data starts with a particular alignment relative to the start of
 the file.